  This update uses Tony Vroon's <tony@vroon.org>
  Closes #32694.

  08 Nov 2003; Chuck Short <zul@gentoo.org> files/eggdrop-installer:
  Fixed typo in eggdrop-installer, closes #32980.

  12 Oct 2003; Chuck Short <zul@gentoo.org> eggdrop-1.6.15.ebuild,
  files/eggdrop-installer:
